536
00:38:26,940 --> 00:38:33,099
[SPEAKER_00] A mi danas još možemo staviti televizija, internet, mobitel.

537
00:38:33,099 --> 00:38:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite sad ovo.

538
00:38:37,059 --> 00:38:42,199
[SPEAKER_00] Istovrstnost proizvoda stvara često konfuziju u našem odlučivanju.

539
00:38:42,199 --> 00:38:46,079
