540
00:38:46,079 --> 00:38:47,139
[SPEAKER_00] vam vidjeti onu recenziju.

541
00:38:47,139 --> 00:38:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ali se ona spašava lažnom slobodom u izboru.

542
00:38:53,559 --> 00:38:55,960
