551
00:39:35,019 --> 00:39:38,320
[SPEAKER_00] Šta idemo samo go with the flow?

552
00:39:38,320 --> 00:39:43,420
[SPEAKER_00] Kud svi tudi mali, jel, perica.

553
00:39:43,420 --> 00:39:47,739
