634
00:45:58,659 --> 00:46:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, to je nagrada.

635
00:46:04,059 --> 00:46:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] I četvrto, ono što je jako bitno usaditi djeci,

636
00:46:08,039 --> 00:46:12,960
