652
00:47:23,139 --> 00:47:29,219
[SPEAKER_00] On bi jako htio, volio igrati PlayStation, pa jel bi ti njemu dao?

653
00:47:29,219 --> 00:47:30,719
[SPEAKER_00] Nije rekla posuditi, dao.

654
00:47:30,719 --> 00:47:33,960
[SPEAKER_00] A ja sam dao.

655
00:47:33,960 --> 00:47:35,280
[SPEAKER_00] Jesam dao sam.

656
00:47:35,280 --> 00:47:36,719
